OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FJulie Devey, Carole Gould and Elaine
OL,8,FNewborough's daughters were all killed
OL,9,Fin violent domestic attacks within the
OL,10,Fhome. They regard this 10 year gap as
OL,11,Fan outrage, calling for sentencing for
OL,12,Fdomestic homicides to be increased.
OL,14,FTheir campaign has influenced a
OL,15,Fgovernment public consultation on
OL,16,Fwhether there should be a change in
OL,17,Fthe law (). With it due to end on the
OL,18,F4th of March. ITV Tonight reporter
OL,19,FJulie Etchingham has been
OL,20,Finvestigating, whose side is the law
OL,21,Fon?
