OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FJulie Devey's daughter, Poppy, was
OL,8,Fjust 24 when she was murdered by her
OL,9,Fex-boyfriend, Joe Atkinson, in their
OL,10,FLeeds flat in 2019. He inflicted more
OL,11,Fthan 70 knife and stab wounds on Poppy
OL,12,Fusing a knife from their kitchen,
OL,13,Fresulting in over 100 injuries.
OL,15,FCarole Gould's daughter Ellie was only
OL,16,F17 when she was murdered by her ex-
OL,17,Fboyfriend in her home in 2019. 17 year
OL,18,Fold Thomas Griffiths stabbed Ellie 13
OL,19,Ftimes in the neck.
