OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FElaine Newborough joined Julie and
OL,8,FCarole's campaign for tougher
OL,9,Fsentences in domestic homicide cases
OL,10,Fafter her daughter Megan was brutally
OL,11,Fmurdered by her work colleague. Megan,
OL,12,F23, was strangled and had her throat
OL,13,Fcut 14 times by Ross McCullam at his
OL,14,Fhome in Leicestershire in 2021.
