OL,7,FThe insidious often subtle nature of
OL,8,Fsuch control means it can be hard for
OL,9,Fwomen to realise the growing danger
OL,10,Fthey are in.
OL,12,FProf Jane Monkton-Smith, Forensic
OL,13,FCriminologist specialising in Domestic
OL,14,FHomicide said "Coercive control is the
OL,15,Fsingle biggest risk marker for future
OL,16,Fserious harm and homicide, the red
OL,17,Fflags start really, really early."
