OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FEarly intervention in abusive
OL,8,Frelationships can save lives and with
OL,9,Fthis in mind the government made
OL,10,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour a
OL,11,Fcriminal offence in 2015.
OL,13,FProf Jane Monkton-Smith suggests
OL,14,F"There is a trigger event that may
OL,15,Fprecede serious harm or homicide. In
OL,16,Fnearly every case that trigger event
OL,17,Fwill be separation."
