OL,3,CJulie Etchingham looks at how the
OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FJulie visited a refuge called 'I
OL,8,FChoose Freedom' where they house women
OL,9,Fat very high risk of being murdered by
OL,10,Fa current or former partner. She
OL,11,Flearns that every room is taken,
OL,12,Fleaving the refuge unable to take in
OL,13,Fmore women who are desperately at risk.
OL,15,FTheir CEO Emma told Julie: "A social
OL,16,Fworker is trying to get a pregnant mum
OL,17,Finto us and we just haven't got the
OL,18,Fcapacity. So on average, we're still
OL,19,Fturning away about seven families for
OL,20,Feach referral that we get, which is
OL,21,Fjust heartbreaking."
