OL,3,CJulie Etchingham looks at how the
OL,4,Cgovernment are tackling violence
OL,5,Cagainst women
OL,7,FAt the 'I Choose Freedom' refuge, CEO
OL,8,FEmma is struggling to stay afloat: "we
OL,9,Fcurrently are facing huge deficits
OL,10,Fwithin our budget for the next year.
OL,11,FI've had to let go of three members of
OL,12,Fstaff this week and we currently don't
OL,13,Fhave a secure future."
OL,15,FAnd without refuges, she feels a lot
OL,16,Fof people will be left in grave
OL,17,Fdanger. Emma told Julie: "I would be
OL,18,Fvery surprised if we don't see a large
OL,19,Fpeak in domestic homicide if there is
OL,20,Fnot long term sustainable funding
OL,21,Fprovided for services like ours."
