OL,7,FIf you are experiencing domestic abuse
OL,8,Fand need immediate help, ask for 'ANI'
OL,9,Fin a participating pharmacy. 'ANI'
OL,10,Fstands for Action Needed Immediately
OL,11,Fbut also phonetically sounds like the
OL,12,Fname Annie. If a pharmacy has the 'Ask
OL,13,Ffor ANI' logo on display, it means
OL,14,Fthey're ready to help. They will offer
OL,15,Fyou a private space, provide a phone
OL,16,Fand ask if you need support from the
OL,17,Fpolice or other domestic abuse support
OL,18,Fservices.
